short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: TabMate is an experimental browser extension intended to solve the “too many tabs” problem with the power of AI.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
TabMate automatically categorizes all browser tabs into topic groups based on the web page content. You can create custom Smart Groups to fine-tune its accuracy, as well as Locked Groups to manually organize tab collections.

Most of the actions in TabMate can be performed using keyboard only. 

TabMate is currently in Beta. Please help us improve TabMate by submitting your feedback and suggestions on our subreddit. (r/tabmate)
